tistics" style=3D"text-align:left"><b><strong>Machine Learning (ML) &amp; S=
tatistics</strong></b></h3><ul><li value=3D"1"><span>Used for model evaluat=
ion.&nbsp;Accuracy/F1-scores of ML models over test sets converge to normal=
ity, enabling comparison via confidence intervals.</span></li><li value=3D"=
2"><span>Stochastic Gradient Descent (SGD)</span><b><strong>:</strong></b><=
span>&nbsp;Batch gradients are averages of random samples =E2=86=92 approxi=
